{"tid":699584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：三隻醉貓擒的士　踢又踩","createTime":"2018-06-12T16:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T17:02:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0681248fe5c72d68ae64943fe9958d75fd2a26ee","tid":699584,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20418231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20418231&d=JQD8j6zJUJvgyHEPV5JzaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=512223ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20418231&h=9dcccdfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20418231</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月12日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：三隻醉貓擒的士　踢又踩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/a12a03a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2Fa12a03a.gif&h=6cc3c33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■其中一隻醉貓擒上車頭冚，踢爛大銀幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個57歲姓曹的哥好黑仔！前晚（10號）佢揸的士經過灣仔道與天樂里交界停燈位，點知遇着三隻南亞醉貓，喺雙黃線夾硬要上的士，佢唔肯開門，話晒今個月1號起喺限制區上落客，俾人捉到嘅話，張牛肉乾盛惠560蚊㗎喎。三隻醉貓上唔到車發爛渣踢車門，其中一人仲擒上的士車頂踩爛個燈箱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/a12a03b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2Fa12a03b.gif&h=e24cc4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■另一個坐喺的士前面唔畀開車。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/a12a03c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2Fa12a03c.gif&h=2ee6c442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路過同鄉影低惡行<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢失平衡由車頂跌落地，起番身又爬上車頭冚，摩打腳咁踢到的士大銀幕變蜘蛛網，另一個就坐喺的士前面馬路唔畀的哥，開車。路過嘅同鄉李先生影低晒佢哋失禮鄉親嘅惡行，的哥一直喺車入面打電話，相信佢報警。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係同鄉，李先生大義凜然咁話同鄉唔啱：「香港有法律，唔應該毀壞的士，用咁暴力嘅方法！好心痛，我哋係土生土長，應該貢獻社會，想做一個好形象畀香港，當呢個係自己個家&hellip;&hellip;你一個南亞裔做呢啲行為，全世界就會覺得個個都係一樣！」<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，前晚9點幾，灣仔天樂里同灣仔道交界，一名南亞漢偕兩友人想坐上的士不遂，跳上的士、又拍又打整爛車窗，的士司機報警，警察到場拉咗一個48歲南亞漢涉嫌刑毀。的哥同阿sir講，喺燈位之前嗰三個人曾經走出馬路攔截佢架車，佢已經扭軚避開，但佢哋仲追上嚟。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：交通黑點證生死相許　新人馬路影婚照<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：霸𨋢搬屋工踢傷女保安"},{"pid":"686b9de5fb59125b38efaf0a80a75392d04e4ed6","tid":699584,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"的佢老母哥咩？"},{"pid":"769fe32f7b4158158251af25860bccb60b98e848","tid":699584,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"又係蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9ca4ed6a973cc68eac0c85d1458f066224b0db","tid":699584,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"的佢老母"}]}